                <head>No. 254.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Messrs. <persName type="from">Cushing and McKenney</persName>
                        to Mr. <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Portland, Me.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1886-07-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 3, 1886</date>. [Received July—.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Our schooner City Point seized in Shelburne, Nova Scotia, for taking in water and
                    allowing men ashore before reporting. Please give instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>CUSHING &amp; McKENNEY.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
